      <h2>Daily Horoscope for All 12 Zodiac Signs</h2>
      
      <h3>Aries Daily Horoscope (March 21 - April 19)</h3>
      <p>As a fire sign, <strong>Aries horoscope today</strong> often focuses on initiative, leadership, and new beginnings. Check your personalized Aries daily horoscope for insights on career opportunities and romantic prospects.</p>
      
      <h3>Taurus Daily Horoscope (April 20 - May 20)</h3>
      <p>The <strong>Taurus daily horoscope</strong> typically emphasizes stability, finances, and sensual pleasures. Your earth sign energy grounds you in practical matters today.</p>
      
      <h3>Gemini Daily Horoscope (May 21 - June 20)</h3>
      <p>Communication is key in today's <strong>Gemini horoscope</strong>. As an air sign, you thrive on mental stimulation and social connections.</p>
      
      <h3>Cancer Daily Horoscope (June 21 - July 22)</h3>
      <p>Your <strong>Cancer daily horoscope</strong> focuses on home, family, and emotional security. The Moon rules your sign, making daily lunar movements especially significant.</p>
      
      <h3>Leo Daily Horoscope (July 23 - August 22)</h3>
      <p>The <strong>Leo horoscope today</strong> shines light on creativity, self-expression, and recognition. Your solar energy attracts attention and opportunities.</p>
      
