      <p>Career and ambition drive the <strong>Capricorn daily horoscope</strong>. Your disciplined approach leads to lasting achievements.</p>
      
      <h3>Aquarius Daily Horoscope (January 20 - February 18)</h3>
      <p>Innovation and humanitarian ideals shape your <strong>Aquarius horoscope today</strong>. Embrace your unique perspective.</p>
      
      <h3>Pisces Daily Horoscope (February 19 - March 20)</h3>
      <p>Intuition and creativity flow through the <strong>Pisces daily horoscope</strong>. Trust your inner guidance for today's decisions.</p>
      
      <h2>Get Your Personalized Daily Horoscope</h2>
      <p>While general <strong>daily horoscope predictions</strong> offer valuable insights, a personalized reading based on your exact birth data provides much more accurate guidance. At Astralo, we create custom horoscope readings that consider your complete natal chart, including your rising sign and Moon placement.</p>
      
      <h2>Why Choose Personalized Over Generic Horoscopes?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accuracy</strong>: Based on your exact birth time and location</li>
        <li><strong>Depth</strong>: Considers all planetary aspects, not just your Sun sign</li>
        <li><strong>Relevance</strong>: Tailored advice for your specific life circumstances</li>
        <li><strong>Timing</strong>: Precise predictions for optimal decision-making</li>
      </ul>
    `
  },
  'zodiac-compatibility-complete-guide': {
    title: 'Zodiac Sign Compatibility: The Ultimate Love Match Guide 2024',
    metaDescription: 'Discover your zodiac compatibility with our complete guide. Find the best love matches for Aries, Taurus, Gemini, Cancer, Leo, Virgo, Libra, Scorpio, Sagittarius, Capricorn, Aquarius & Pisces.',
    keywords: 'zodiac compatibility, love horoscope, star sign compatibility, zodiac love match, astrological compatibility, relationship horoscope',
    date: '2024-12-18',
    readTime: '12 min',
    category: 'Love & Relationships',
    author: 'Astralo Team',
    content: `
      <h2>Understanding Zodiac Compatibility</h2>
      <p><strong>Zodiac compatibility</strong> is the study of how different astrological signs interact in relationships. Whether you're looking for your perfect <strong>love match</strong> or trying to understand your current relationship better, understanding <strong>star sign compatibility</strong> can provide valuable insights.</p>
      
      <h2>The Elements of Compatibility</h2>
      <p>In astrology, zodiac signs are grouped by elements, which play a crucial role in <strong>astrological compatibility</strong>:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Fire Signs (Aries, Leo, Sagittarius)</strong>: Passionate, energetic, and adventurous</li>
        <li><strong>Earth Signs (Taurus, Virgo, Capricorn)</strong>: Practical, grounded, and reliable</li>
        <li><strong>Air Signs (Gemini, Libra, Aquarius)</strong>: Intellectual, communicative, and social</li>
