      <p><strong>Gemini zodiac compatibility</strong> excels with Libra and Aquarius (air signs) and Aries and Leo (fire signs). The Gemini-Libra match brings intellectual stimulation and social harmony.</p>
      
      <h2>Partner Compatibility Reading</h2>
      <p>For a complete understanding of your <strong>relationship compatibility</strong>, consider a personalized partner horoscope. At Astralo, we analyze both partners' birth charts to reveal:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Emotional compatibility and communication styles</li>
        <li>Long-term relationship potential</li>
        <li>Areas of harmony and potential challenges</li>
        <li>Timing for major relationship milestones</li>
      </ul>
    `
  },
  'birth-chart-reading-explained': {
    title: 'Birth Chart Reading: How to Understand Your Natal Chart',
    metaDescription: 'Learn how to read your birth chart. Complete natal chart guide explaining planets, houses, aspects, and how to interpret your astrological chart for personality insights.',
    keywords: 'birth chart, natal chart, astrology chart, horoscope chart, birth chart reading, natal chart interpretation',
    date: '2024-12-15',
    readTime: '10 min',
    category: 'Astrology Basics',
    author: 'Astralo Team',
    content: `
      <h2>What is a Birth Chart?</h2>
      <p>A <strong>birth chart</strong> (also called a <strong>natal chart</strong>) is a map of where all the planets were at the exact moment you were born. This <strong>astrological chart</strong> serves as your cosmic fingerprint, revealing your personality, strengths, challenges, and life path.</p>
      
      <h2>Key Components of Your Natal Chart</h2>
      
      <h3>The Planets</h3>
      <p>Each planet in your <strong>birth chart reading</strong> represents a different aspect of your personality:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Sun</strong>: Your core identity and ego</li>
        <li><strong>Moon</strong>: Your emotions and inner self</li>
        <li><strong>Mercury</strong>: Communication and thinking</li>
        <li><strong>Venus</strong>: Love, beauty, and values</li>
        <li><strong>Mars</strong>: Action, energy, and desire</li>
        <li><strong>Jupiter</strong>: Expansion, luck, and wisdom</li>
        <li><strong>Saturn</strong>: Discipline, responsibility, and karma</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>The 12 Houses</h3>
      <p>The houses in your <strong>natal chart interpretation</strong> represent different life areas, from self-image (1st house) to spirituality (12th house).</p>
      
      <h3>Aspects</h3>
      <p>Aspects are the angles between planets, showing how different parts of your personality interact. Conjunctions, trines, and sextiles are harmonious, while squares and oppositions indicate tension and growth opportunities.</p>
      
      <h2>Get Your Personal Birth Chart Reading</h2>
      <p>Understanding your <strong>horoscope chart</strong> requires expertise. Our personalized birth chart readings at Astralo provide detailed interpretations tailored specifically to you.</p>
    `
  },
  'weekly-horoscope-predictions': {
    title: 'Weekly Horoscope: What the Stars Predict for This Week',
    metaDescription: 'Get your weekly horoscope predictions for all zodiac signs. Discover love, career, and life forecasts for Aries through Pisces this week.',
    keywords: 'weekly horoscope, horoscope this week, weekly zodiac, weekly astrology, horoscope predictions weekly',
    date: '2024-12-22',
    readTime: '6 min',
    category: 'Horoscopes',
    author: 'Astralo Team',
    content: `
      <h2>Your Weekly Horoscope Overview</h2>
      <p>Welcome to your <strong>weekly horoscope</strong> forecast! This week brings powerful planetary alignments that will affect all zodiac signs differently. Read on to discover what the stars have in store for your <strong>horoscope this week</strong>.</p>
      
      <h2>Weekly Zodiac Predictions</h2>
      <p>Our <strong>weekly astrology</strong> forecasts consider the major planetary transits affecting each sign, including the Moon's journey through the zodiac, Mercury's communications, and Venus's influence on love and finances.</p>
      
      <h2>Get a Detailed Weekly Reading</h2>
      <p>For more in-depth <strong>weekly horoscope predictions</strong>, consider our personalized weekly horoscope that takes your exact birth data into account for maximum accuracy.</p>
    `
  },
  'monthly-horoscope-january-2025': {
    title: 'Monthly Horoscope January 2025: All Zodiac Sign Predictions',
    metaDescription: 'January 2025 monthly horoscope for all zodiac signs. Complete astrological forecast for love, career, health, and finances in the new year.',
    keywords: 'monthly horoscope, horoscope january 2025, monthly zodiac, horoscope 2025, monthly astrology forecast',
    date: '2024-12-24',
    readTime: '15 min',
    category: 'Horoscopes',
    author: 'Astralo Team',
    content: `
      <h2>January 2025 Monthly Horoscope</h2>
      <p>Welcome to your <strong>monthly horoscope for January 2025</strong>! The new year begins with powerful cosmic energy as several planets shift positions. This comprehensive <strong>monthly astrology forecast</strong> covers all 12 zodiac signs.</p>
      
      <h2>Key Astrological Events in January 2025</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>New Moon in Capricorn</strong>: New beginnings in career and goals</li>
        <li><strong>Full Moon in Cancer</strong>: Emotional revelations and family focus</li>
        <li><strong>Mercury enters Aquarius</strong>: Innovative thinking and communication</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Get Your Complete 2025 Horoscope</h2>
      <p>For a detailed <strong>horoscope 2025</strong> forecast personalized to your birth chart, order your monthly horoscope from Astralo today.</p>
    `
  },
  'love-horoscope-relationship-advice': {
    title: 'Love Horoscope 2024: Relationship Predictions for Every Sign',
    metaDescription: 'Get your love horoscope predictions. Discover romantic compatibility, relationship timing, and love advice for all zodiac signs in 2024.',
    keywords: 'love horoscope, relationship horoscope, love astrology, romantic horoscope, love predictions, zodiac love',
    date: '2024-12-10',
    readTime: '9 min',
    category: 'Love & Relationships',
    author: 'Astralo Team',
    content: `
      <h2>Your Love Horoscope Guide</h2>
      <p>Looking for love in the stars? Your <strong>love horoscope</strong> can reveal important insights about your romantic life, from finding your soulmate to strengthening existing relationships. Our <strong>relationship horoscope</strong> predictions help you navigate the complex world of love and romance.</p>
      
      <h2>Venus and Your Love Life</h2>
      <p>In <strong>love astrology</strong>, Venus is the planet of love, beauty, and attraction. Understanding Venus's placement in your chart and its current transits provides valuable insights into your <strong>romantic horoscope</strong>.</p>
      
      <h2>Partner Compatibility Analysis</h2>
      <p>For a complete understanding of your relationship dynamics, consider our partner horoscope service. We analyze both partners' charts to reveal deep compatibility insights.</p>
    `
  }
};

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return Object.keys(blogPosts).map(slug => ({ params: { slug } }));
}

const { slug } = Astro.params;
const post = blogPosts[slug];

if (!post) {
  return Astro.redirect('/blog');
}

// Related posts (exclude current)
const relatedPosts = Object.entries(blogPosts)
  .filter(([s, p]) => s !== slug && p.category === post.category)
  .slice(0, 2);
---

<Layout 
  title={`${post.title} | Astralo Blog`}
  description={post.metaDescription}
  keywords={post.keywords}
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col relative z-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="glass-strong border-b border-white/10 sticky top-0 z-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-colors group">
            <ArrowLeft class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
            <span class="text-sm">Back to Blog</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/"><img src="/logo.png" alt="Astralo" class="h-9" /></a>
          <div class="w-24"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Article -->
    <main class="flex-1 px-4 py-12">
      <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Meta -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-6 text-sm">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-500/20 text-amber-400 rounded-full">{post.category}</span>
          <span class="text-white/50 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Calendar class="w-4 h-4" />
            {new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { month: 'long', day: 'numeric', year: 'numeric' })}
          </span>
          <span class="text-white/50 flex items-center gap-2">
            <Clock class="w-4 h-4" />
            {post.readTime} read
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Title -->
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          {post.title}
        </h1>

        <!-- Author -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8 pb-8 border-b border-white/10">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-amber-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <Star class="w-5 h-5 text-white" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-white font-medium">{post.author}</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Expert Astrologer</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div 
          class="prose prose-lg prose-invert max-w-none
            prose-headings:text-white prose-headings:font-bold
            prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4
            prose-h3:text-xl prose-h3:mt-8 prose-h3:mb-3
            prose-p:text-white/80 prose-p:leading-relaxed prose-p:mb-4
            prose-strong:text-amber-200
            prose-ul:text-white/80 prose-li:mb-2
            prose-a:text-amber-400 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline"
          set:html={post.content}
        />

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="mt-12 glass-strong rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-amber-500/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Get Your Personalized Horoscope</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">Based on your exact birth data for maximum accuracy</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-amber-500 text-black font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors">
            <Star class="w-5 h-5" />
            Order Now - 50% OFF
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Related Posts -->
        {relatedPosts.length > 0 && (
          <div class="mt-12">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Related Articles</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              {relatedPosts.map(([s, p]) => (
                <a href={`/blog/${s}`} class="glass rounded-xl p-5 block hover:border-amber-500/30 border border-white/10 transition-all group">
                  <span class="text-amber-400 text-xs">{p.category}</span>
                  <h4 class="text-white font-medium mt-1 group-hover:text-amber-200 transition-colors">{p.title}</h4>
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        )}
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer lang="en" />
  </div>
</Layout>
